{"tid":2439203,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"放貓咪入袋問題","createTime":"2021-03-09T05:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T05:21:56.000Z","uid":93445,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"57bfc0aa3f190dd9c3b23f8bac9f1e322a59ee76","tid":2439203,"uid":93445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"女友本身約左晏晝帶主子絕育<br />\n但佢掙扎得好勁 搞左好耐都放唔到入袋<br />\n而家佢好惡又ha氣 仲跳左上櫃頂唔戲落嚟<br />\n迫住要同醫生改期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先交代一下主子背景<br />\n主子而家就黎一歲 喺大概大半年前向一對夫婦領養既<br />\n<br />\n咁領養個日去對夫婦屋企接主子<br />\n佢地本身都養左五六隻狗加五六隻貓<br />\n未入屋啲狗就已經好熱情不停咁吠 幾大聲下<br />\n好慘既係我地領養個隻貓個時先兩個月大 但就日日俾啲狗聲嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好慘<br />\n咁夫婦係主人房拎貓咪出黎個時都俾貓咪整損左<br />\n<br />\n初初接返黎都用左好一段時間先敢行出黎見人同食野<br />\n加上本身有隻大啲既貓係到 好驚佢會俾蝦<br />\n好彩佢地而家相處得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但主子到而家都係唔俾抱 唔知關唔關上述既陰影事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主子自發情後開始四圍喺啲衫上面小便 間唔時先用返廁所<br />\n而家唯有等主子發完下一個cycle既情再book醫生<br />\n想問下巴絲們有冇咩方法可以解決入袋問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifBOEcT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifBOEcT.png&h=f14781d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae1fe5c4f71bf80b75e2c9bb8a2895af7893f5c7","tid":2439203,"uid":174281,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"57bfc0aa3f190dd9c3b23f8bac9f1e322a59ee76","tid":2439203,"uid":93445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"女友本身約左晏晝帶主子絕育<br />\n但佢掙扎得好勁 搞左好耐都放唔到入袋<br />\n而家佢好惡又ha氣 仲跳左上櫃頂唔戲落嚟<br />\n迫住要同醫生改期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先交代一下主子背景<br />\n主子而家就黎一歲 喺大概大半年前向一對夫婦領養既<br />\n<br />\n咁領養個日去對夫婦屋企接主子<br />\n佢地本身都養左五六隻狗加五六隻貓<br />\n未入屋啲狗就已經好熱情不停咁吠 幾大聲下<br />\n好慘既係我地領養個隻貓個時先兩個月大 但就日日俾啲狗聲嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好慘<br />\n咁夫婦係主人房拎貓咪出黎個時都俾貓咪整損左<br />\n<br />\n初初接返黎都用左好一段時間先敢行出黎見人同食野<br />\n加上本身有隻大啲既貓係到 好驚佢會俾蝦<br />\n好彩佢地而家相處得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但主子到而家都係唔俾抱 唔知關唔關上述既陰影事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主子自發情後開始四圍喺啲衫上面小便 間唔時先用返廁所<br />\n而家唯有等主子發完下一個cycle既情再book醫生<br />\n想問下巴絲們有冇咩方法可以解決入袋問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifBOEcT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifBOEcT.png&h=f14781d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"可以試下平時多啲引佢入袋玩<br />\n或者當佢喺袋入面個陣 俾多啲甜頭佢（餵下零食之類）<br />\n等佢習慣咗知道原來入袋都幾好<br />\n雖然唔知幫唔幫到樓主 不過一試無妨<br />\n<br />\n利申：養緊四隻貓"},{"pid":"13c825a960c710bf91c02dfba78aa22f5a5634cd","tid":2439203,"uid":60733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:37:35.000Z","msg":"平時就要放個袋出黎比佢習慣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放有佢味d野入袋 擺返357日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e57f5b0490d6b3e9b3d25886cb08f5c1006276d","tid":2439203,"uid":93445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"好既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放個袋係廳等佢習慣下先"},{"pid":"272b6a906ca40d6a94705c3b7cf2f5035abf57d8","tid":2439203,"uid":169307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"長放係度佢就直程有時會入去嫁啦 再唔得放零食入去試下"},{"pid":"5752c8cf1c1edd05c1befb61e5ee2df99ef17772","tid":2439203,"uid":196485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"或者試下用飛機籠 關門易過拉拉鍊"},{"pid":"646e49484232146afc3484e2bd2a383314dc4505","tid":2439203,"uid":62597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"樓主當初用左幾耐時間令到隻貓入屋後適應到"},{"pid":"73451ade9cfe40979940b74a18f7797927700d52","tid":2439203,"uid":170079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"用飛機籠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 袋難入過籠咁多,你個隻咁抗拒你仲要用袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e67a9c2b00d2aa84f743f93d0ef9a9682048526","tid":2439203,"uid":59839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:05:18.000Z","msg":"大力d就得<br />\n一個人打開袋<br />\n一個人塞佢入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f47ec3a04416c93eae1857a68911b1861b6266","tid":2439203,"uid":93445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"646e49484232146afc3484e2bd2a383314dc4505","tid":2439203,"uid":62597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"樓主當初用左幾耐時間令到隻貓入屋後適應到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:50:42.000Z","msg":"都講緊一個月"},{"pid":"6b2580acb802e50d7890d4a074f15716ade628b6","tid":2439203,"uid":93445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73451ade9cfe40979940b74a18f7797927700d52","tid":2439203,"uid":170079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"用飛機籠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 袋難入過籠咁多,你個隻咁抗拒你仲要用袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"黎緊都會放個籠係廳 等佢習慣一排先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1314ae7041b09dda4b0d7a85b909a4d5ee0c061","tid":2439203,"uid":18772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"野食 抱 野食 抱 野食 抱"},{"pid":"f918d8ca886c717b3f921e3a7904feee33086e71","tid":2439203,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl